title: Doctor Who Magazine Winter Special 1992
description:
To view this, you need CDisplay. Please leave a comment if you need help or want to know where to get this program, but you can also google it.

This is for us fans of the original series, but new viewers are welcome to come with us and explore the rich and vast history of the Doctor's past and his people.

A little "Thank You" would be nice and it would prompt me to continue uploading Doctor Who stuff for you guys. I have many a treasure that I've found on the internet lately.
